oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: "Performance - Family Program: Songwriting Camp Showcase - 2017-06-17 "
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performances of original songs written by young songwriters during summer songwriting camp from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on June 17, 2017.
